#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktimer; is an application that lets you start an application after a "
"certain amount of time has passed."
msgstr ""
"&ktimer; je aplikace, která umožňuje spustit jinou aplikaci po zadaném "
"časovém intervalu."

